{"article_id":"FzNy7kdwz1GLEVHg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A grandmother 's bones were broken .","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"A pregnant woman was violently thrown to the ground .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Millions of dollars were paid out to numerous victims of police brutality .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"So I join all","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"who say","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that protests in Baltimore should remain peaceful ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"and I will continue to withhold judgment about Gray 's death","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"until more facts are known .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"But I also insist","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that Baltimore protests are appropriate","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"regardless of what happened to Freddie Gray ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"as is more federal scrutiny and intervention .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Although much was rightly made of Ferguson 's racially unrepresentative local leadership ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"the presence of a black mayor and a diverse city council has not solved Baltimore 's police problem ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"partly because the DOJ responded to revelations of epidemic brutality with less than the full-scale civil rights probe","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that some residents requested","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"and because Maryland pols have thwarted reform bills","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"urged by city leaders .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"There are so many good reasons for locals to be outraged .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"The Baltimore Sun 's article shows why in detail .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"And a few choice excerpts are the best beginning in this attempt","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"to contextualize the ongoing protests within recent history .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"$ 5.7 million is the amount","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"the city paid to victims of brutality between 2011 and 2014 .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"And","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"as huge","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"as that figure is ,","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"the more staggering number in the article is this one :","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"`` Over the past four years , more than 100 people have won court judgments or settlements","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"related to allegations of brutality and civil-rights violations . ''","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"What tiny percentage of the unjustly beaten win formal legal judgments ?","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"If you 're imagining","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"that they were all men in their twenties ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"think again :","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Victims include a 15-year-old boy","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"riding a dirt bike ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"a 26-year-old pregnant accountant","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"who had witnessed a beating ,","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"a 50-year-old woman","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"selling church raffle tickets ,","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"a 65-year-old church deacon","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"rolling a cigarette","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"and an 87-year-old grandmother","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"aiding her wounded grandson .","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"Those cases detail a frightful human toll .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Officers have battered dozens of residents","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"who suffered broken bones","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"- jaws , noses , arms , legs , ankles -","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"head trauma , organ failure , and even death ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"coming during questionable arrests .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Some residents were beaten","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"while handcuffed ;","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"others were thrown to the pavement .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"The 87-year-old grandmother was named Venus Green .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"A former teacher with two college degrees ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"she spent her retirement years as a foster parent for needy children .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"She was on her porch one day","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"when her grandson ran up","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"crying for an ambulance .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"The article goes on to tell her story from a legal document in her successful lawsuit :","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Paramedics and police responded to the emergency call ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"but the white officer became hostile .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"\" What happened ?","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"Who shot you ? \"","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"Green recalled the officer saying to her grandson ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"according to an 11-page letter","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"in which she detailed the incident for her lawyer .","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"Excerpts from the letter were included in her lawsuit .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"\" You ' re lying .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"You know","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"you were shot inside that house .","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"We ain ' t going to help you","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"because you are lying. \"","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"\" Mister , he isn ' t lying , \"","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"replied Green ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"who had no criminal record .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"\" He came from down that way running ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"calling me to call the ambulance. \"","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"The officer ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"who is not identified in the lawsuit ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"wanted to go into the basement ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"but Green demanded a warrant .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Her grandson kept two dogs downstairs","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"and she feared","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"they would attack .","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"The officer unhooked the lock ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"but Green latched it .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"He shoved Green against the wall .","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"She hit the wooden floor .","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"\" Bitch , you ain ' t no better than any of the other old black bitches","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"I have locked up , \"","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"Green recalled the officer saying","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"as he stood over her .","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"\" He pulled me up ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"pushed me in the dining room over the couch ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"put his knees in my back ,","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"twisted my arms and wrist","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"and put handcuffs on my hands","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"and threw me face down on the couch. \"","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"After pulling Green to her feet ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"the officer told her","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"she was under arrest .","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"Green complained of pain .","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"\" My neck and shoulder are hurting , \"","depth":16},{"id":104,"text":"Green told him .","depth":16},{"id":105,"text":"\" Please take these handcuffs off. \"","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"An African-American officer then walked in the house ,","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"saw her sobbing","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"and asked","depth":17},{"id":109,"text":"that the handcuffs be removed","depth":18},{"id":110,"text":"since Green wasn ' t violent .","depth":18},{"id":111,"text":"The cuffs came off ,","depth":16},{"id":112,"text":"and Green didn ' t face any charges .","depth":16},{"id":113,"text":"But a broken shoulder tormented her for months .","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"When pondering the fact","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"that Baltimore paid out $ 5.7 million in brutality settlements over four years ,","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"consider","depth":4},{"id":117,"text":"that the payout in this case was just $ 95,000 .","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"( For the story of the pregnant woman and many others , the full article is here . )","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":237,"left":232,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":130,"right":231,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":121,"right":129,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":120,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":125,"right":128,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":123,"right":124,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":3,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":8,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":135,"right":230,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":135,"left":131,"right":134,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":132,"right":133,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":132,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":138,"right":229,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":138,"left":18,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":19,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":168,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":160,"right":16